CURRENT VERSION
===============

Version 1.1, April 2016.



TESTING
=======

Pcapteller has been tested on Kali Linux with Python 2.7.



KNOWN ISSUES
============

- DNS response packets are replayed, but in an inconsistent / malformed / corrupted manner.
  It seems like this is caused by Scapy. The issue is under investigation.



